UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc5='Some time ago, Brann sent King Magni an urgent message from Ulduar. He said he\'d found an ancient titan cache with mysterious and important relics. King Wrynn dispatched one of his fastest ships to Northrend to transport the courier. I was to meet him here and examine the tablets, but the courier is nowhere to be seen.$B$BMagni is worried, $N. I haven\'t heard anything about the courier\'s arrival. Would you be willing to travel to Stormwind Harbor and see if he\'s arrived?',objectives_loc5='Bring the Tablets of Earth to Advisor Belgrum in Ironforge.',offerrewardtext_loc5='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Brann himself wrote that he hardly knows their significance, although he did mention something about becoming one with the earth. I will need to confer with my fellow Explorer\'s League scholars to decipher these as soon as possible.$B$BThank you, $N. Without your aid, these tablets would\'ve fallen into enemy hands.' WHERE entry=25180;
UPDATE locales_quest SET details_loc5='I\'m expecting the arrival of a courier traveling from Northrend. He\'s carrying a collection of ancient titan treasures, ones I\'m hoping will shed light on my troubling visions. The shaman should\'ve arrived on one of the recent zeppelin flights and I\'m starting to get worried.$B$BHe was to meet me by the zeppelin tower southwest of Orgrimmar\'s gates, but I don\'t want to miss my audience with the warchief. Would you be willing to look for the courier and see what\'s delaying him?',objectives_loc5='Bring the Tablets of Fire to Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc5='Why would Twilight\'s Hammer take an interest in these tablets? Their contents are a mystery to our most learned scholars and deciphering them will take some time. If Twilight\'s Hammer knows about these relics and desires them, what more are they plotting?$B$BWe are most fortunate that you protected them from capture, $N.' WHERE entry=25181;
